text: Walter Gabathuler (born 20 June 1954) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
